bharya bhartalu ( telugu : భార్యాభర్తలు ; english : wife & husband ) is a 1961 telugu , drama film , produced by a. v. subba rao on prasad art pictures banner and directed by k.pratyagatma . starring akkineni nageshwara rao , krishna kumari in the lead roles and music composed by s. rajeswara rao . the film was adapted from tamil novel pennmanam by lakshmi tripurasundari . it was remade in tamil as iruvar ullam ( 1963 ) by l. v. prasad starring sivaji ganesan and hindi as hamrahi ( 1963 ) by t. prakash rao starring rajendra kumar , jamuna in pivotal roles .